Summary: a group of 9 triangle shape white light all in a trriangle
divs: Sighting Detailsmy wife was driving we were coming home from a night at little six casino. it was around 3 AM in the morning. we were driving my wife that is, going north on highway 169 we were at anderson lake on 169 south of 494. She said look to the right out are car window about 4 blocks away were 9 white triangle and they were in a triangle shape. we were still driving for about 10 second and then they all disappear. For years we talk about that night. but in the last few years I read about what was seen in the area back in 1997
